T02TD1275E:102b-1: ma h'a aa bhi she ka tri kra ma n'a ma /
T02TD1275E:102b-3: dbang chen po rim pa gsum pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD1275E:102b-4: dpal kye rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1275E:102b-5: pra yi ye shes sgrub 'dod pas //
T02TD1275E:102b-6: 'dod chos mtshan gnyis shes pa'i mu //
T02TD1275E:102b-7: de shes yul du bya ba ni //
T02TD1275E:102b-8: mig dgug shir mtha' zad rtse //
T02TD1275E:102b-9: chu skyes dga' gnyis dbus su 'dus //
T02TD1275E:102b-10: gsang ba'i sa bcur shes par bya //
T02TD1275E:102b-11: thabs kyi ze 'bru gsum nor bu //
T02TD1275E:102b-12: pra ru 'dod pa sangs rgyas gcig / thur rlung phrad bzlog dbus zhugs pas //
T02TD1275E:102b-14: rtog bral smon lam gzugs su gnyis //
T02TD1275E:102b-15: ra ta'i ti la bzhi 'gyur gyi //
T02TD1275E:102b-16: skad cig cha kun shes byas nas //
T02TD1275E:102b-17: ro bzhi shes pas ro bzhi bya //
T02TD1275E:102b-18: rlung gi sa yi dus su ni //
T02TD1275E:102b-19: h'um phat bskyod pas las rlung me //
T02TD1275E:102b-21: sa yi dus su bzlog la bstun //
T02TD1275E:102b-22: chu tshags rlung gis gzung yi ge //
T02TD1275E:102b-24: ting 'dzin khyad par gyur pa yis //
T02TD1275E:102b-25: gnyis 'dus bha gar rlung bzhi gnon //
T02TD1275E:102b-26: mi g-yo bdud bzhi mnan zhes bya //
T02TD1275E:102b-27: cung zad 'dus par zin pa yis //
T02TD1275E:102b-28: mi rtog dang po'i sa thob bshad //
T02TD1275E:102b-29: brgyad phyed mtha' yi brgyad phyed mthar /
T02TD1275E:102b-30: brag gdung lta bu gnyis phrad de //
T02TD1275E:102b-31: bstan pas ye shes bsam yas shing //
T02TD1275E:102b-32: kun kyang gsal ba dung lta bu //
T02TD1275E:102b-33: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
T02TD1275E:102b-34: yon tan che ba brjod mi lang //
T02TD1275E:102b-35: gal te pra yi nyi ma dag / thig le kha bsgyur sngon bzhin sprad //
T02TD1275E:102b-36: mar ram chu ltar 'dres nus pas //
T02TD1275E:102b-37: so sor gnas kyang rmongs pa med //
T02TD1275E:102b-38: kun rdzob snang ba ma yin te //
T02TD1275E:102b-39: dngos po gnyis kyang rtag tu 'dres //
T02TD1275E:102b-40: sus kyang mthong bar mi nus te //
T02TD1275E:102b-41: yon tan ljags kyis rdzogs pa min //
T02TD1275E:102b-42: bskal par 'jigs dang bral ba med //
T02TD1275E:102b-43: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes sku //
T02TD1275E:103a-2: dbang chen po rim pa gsum pa zhes bya ba rdzogs rim gyi man ngag rdzogs so//
